{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/introduction-to-higher-order-functions-and-callbacks-in-javascript/lab-sorted-index-finder/lab-sorted-index-finder","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"lab-sorted-index-finder","demoType":null,"title":"Izvršiće pronaći konfigurisani model","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovom okruženju ćete kreirati funkciju koja vraća najmanji indeks gde treba uneti vrednost u niz podataka nakon sortiranja po rastućem redosledu.</p>\n<p><strong>Cilj</strong>: Popuni priče korisnika ispod i prođi sve testove kako bi se završio laboratorijum.</p>\n<p><strong>Priče korisnika:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Treba da ima funkciju <code>getIndexToIns</code> koja prima dva argumenta: niz podataka i broj.</li>\n<li>Treba koristiti metodu <code>sort</code> za sortiranje niza podataka po uzlaznom redosledu.</li>\n<li>Tvoja funkcija <code>getIndexToIns</code> treba da vrati najnižu vrednost gde bi trebalo uneti broj koristeći metodu <code>findIndex</code>.</li>\n<li>Tvoja funkcija <code>getIndexToIns</code> treba da uvek vrati broj.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Snipet:</strong>\r\nMetoda za <code>findIndex</code> je metoda napravljena unutar niza podataka u JavaScript. Prima <em>callback</em> funkciju i vraća instancu prvog elementa koji zadovoljava uslov. Sve <code>findIndex</code> i <code>sort</code> su funkcije visokog nivoa.</p>\n<p><strong>Primjeri:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>getIndexToIns([1, 2, 3, 4], 1.5)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>1</code> jer <code>1.5</code> je veće od <code>1</code> (primer <code>0</code>) i manje od <code>2</code> (primer <code>1</code>).</li>\n<li><code>getIndexToIns([20, 3, 5], 19)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>2</code> jer nakon organizovanja u <code>[3, 5, 20]</code>, <code>19</code> je manje od <code>20</code> (primer <code>2</code>) i veće od <code>5</code> (primer <code>1</code>).</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","id":"68a47dcdbce12193caf77012","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":26,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"introduction-to-higher-order-functions-and-callbacks-in-javascript","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/introduction-to-higher-order-functions-and-callbacks-in-javascript/lab-sorted-index-finder/lab-sorted-index-finder"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imaš funkciju <code>getIndexToIns</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFunction(getIndexToIns);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns</code> Treba da uvek vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 35));"},{"text":"<p>Tvoja funkcija mora da koristi metodu <code>sort</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(getIndexToIns.toString(), /\\.sort\\(/);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoja funkcija treba da koristi <code>findIndex</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(getIndexToIns.toString(), /\\.findIndex\\(/);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 35)</code> treba da vrati <code>3</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 35), 3);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 30)</code> treba da vrati <code>2</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([10, 20, 30, 40, 50], 30), 2);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([40, 60], 50)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>1</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([40, 60], 50), 1);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([3, 10, 5], 3)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>0</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([3, 10, 5], 3), 0);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([5, 3, 20, 3], 5)</code> trebalo bi vratiti <code>2</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([5, 3, 20, 3], 5), 2);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([2, 20, 10], 19)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>2</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([2, 20, 10], 19), 2);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([3, 10, 5], 11)</code> treba da vrati <code>3</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([3, 10, 5], 11), 3);"},{"text":"<p><code>getIndexToIns([], 5)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>0</code></p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(getIndexToIns([], 5), 0);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/introduction-to-higher-order-functions-and-callbacks-in-javascript/#lab-sorted-index-finder","dashedName":"lab-sorted-index-finder","certification":"introduction-to-higher-order-functions-and-callbacks-in-javascript","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"introduction-to-higher-order-functions-and-callbacks-in-javascript","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"lab-sorted-index-finder","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-higher-order-functions-and-callbacks-in-javascript/lab-symmetric-difference/lab-symmetric-difference","prevChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-higher-order-functions-and-callbacks-in-javascript/lab-book-organizer/build-a-book-organizer","id":"68a47dcdbce12193caf77012","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":26,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function getIndexToIns(arr, num) {\r\n  const sorted = [...arr].sort((a, b) => a - b);\r\n  const index = sorted.findIndex(el => el >= num);\r\n\r\n  return index === -1 ? sorted.length : index;\r\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/introduction-to-higher-order-functions-and-callbacks-in-javascript/lab-sorted-index-finder/lab-sorted-index-finder"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}